 X-ray cycles we deduce a simple empirical relationship between X-ray\ncyclic modulation and Rossby number, and we also present Swift UV grism spectra\ncovering 2300-6000 {\\AA}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2016 17:57:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-12"}
